com.google.gwt.dev.js
Class JsCoerceIntShift

java.lang.Object
  com.google.gwt.dev.js.JsCoerceIntShift

public class JsCoerceIntShift
extends java.lang.Object

Coerces lhs of right shift operations to int. Necessary for Safari 5 bug https://bugs.webkit.org/show_bug.cgi?id=40367 fixed in http://trac.webkit.org/changeset/60990 -- this should be removed once that fix has been pushed.
